# Security headers for the static host (Cloudflare Pages reads this file from
# the build output; Astro copies public/ into dist/ verbatim). SEC-6.
#
# CSP notes:
# - convex.cloud (https + wss) is the live data connection; convex.site hosts
#   the auth HTTP endpoints the magic link passes through. The *.convex
#   wildcards below are a TEMPLATE only: the build (astro.config.mjs,
#   wai:csp-convex-deployment-origin) rewrites them to the exact deployment
#   origin from PUBLIC_CONVEX_URL, or strips them when it is unset. The file
#   Cloudflare Pages serves from dist/ never contains a Convex wildcard.
# - challenges.cloudflare.com is Turnstile (script + iframe + verify call).
# - Fonts are self-hosted (polish slice); no third-party font origins remain.
# - images.unsplash.com stays allowed until real member photos replace the
#   concept images (owner item).
# - blob: images are the profile-photo preview; data: covers inline SVG uses.
# - 'unsafe-inline' for styles is required by Astro's inlined component styles
#   and React style attributes. Scripts allow 'unsafe-inline' for Astro's small
#   inline bootstraps; tighten to hashes after the polish slice if possible.

/*
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://challenges.cloudflare.com; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; font-src 'self'; img-src 'self' data: blob: https://images.unsplash.com https://*.convex.cloud; connect-src 'self' https://*.convex.cloud wss://*.convex.cloud https://*.convex.site https://challenges.cloudflare.com; frame-src https://challenges.cloudflare.com; object-src 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self'; frame-ancestors 'none'
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=(), payment=()
